Once upon a time, in a hole in the ground there lived one hobbit Joker who actually is 100 years old.
Not a nasty, dirty, wet hole, filled with the ends of worms. And
Alongside him there was a smelly, blunt dwarf Billy, who is 20.0.
dwarf Crook is Joker plus Billy.
